    MaterialSideNav, MaterialSideNavCard, MaterialSideNavDrawer, MaterialSideNavMini, MaterialSideNavPush

    public abstract class AbstractSideNav
extends MaterialWidget
implements JsLoader, HasSelectables, HasInOutDurationTransition, HasSideNavHandlers
    AbstractSideNav handles the creation and Ui logic for different sidenavs, you can easily setup any kind of logic for you sidenav behaviour in setup().
    Author:
    kevzlou7979
